# Local Dev Bootstrap  
- On first run, execute `scripts/install.sh` to setup dependencies.  
- Use `docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d --build --remove-orphans` for dev mode.  
- Update `/etc/hosts` (with sudo) adding:  
127.0.0.1 landing.makesoft.io
127.0.0.1 auth.makesoft.io
127.0.0.1 portal.makesoft.io
127.0.0.1 forum.makesoft.io
127.0.0.1 api.makesoft.io
- After containers up, seed MongoDB with `docker exec mongo ./scripts/seed-db.sh`.  
- Enable code hot-reload mounts in dev mode for frontend/backend.  
- When switching to prod branch, ensure dev hosts entries are cleaned or disabled.